9QYVdz_Plastic bag.png\"></figure><p style=\"text-align:center;\"><span><strong>Plastic Bags</strong></span></p></td><td><figure class=\"image image_resized\" style=\"width:80.13%;\"><img src=\"$url/storage/ckeditor-images/KNwBSIaM_recycle bags.png\"></figure><p style=\"text-align:center;\"><span><strong>Paper or Cloth Bags</strong></span></p></td></tr><tr><td><figure class=\"image image_resized\" style=\"width:74.71%;\"><img src=\"$url/storage/ckeditor-images/232-2322857_see-the-waste-plastic-bottle.png\"></figure><p style=\"text-align:center;\"><span><strong>Plastic Bottles</strong></span></p></td><td><figure class=\"image image_resized\" style=\"width:72.1%;\"><img src=\"$url/storage/ckeditor-images/metal bottles.png\"></figure><p style=\"text-align:center;\"><strong>Metal Bottles</strong></p></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>",
                "answer_km": "<p>ដោយជ្រើសរើសសំភារៈដែលអាចប្រើប្រាស់ឡើងវិញ យើងអាចចូលរួមកាត់បន្ថយបរិមាណសំរាម ដែលត្រូវយកទៅចាក់ចោលនៅ​ទីលានចាក់សំរាម។ ខាងក្រោមនេះជាឧទាហរណ៍មួយចំនួន៖</p><figure class=\"table\"><table><colgroup><col style=\"width:50%;\"><col style=\"width:50%;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><td><p style=\"text-align:center;\"><span><strong>សំភារៈប្លាស្ទិក</strong></span></p></td><td><p style=\"text-align:center;\"><span><strong>សំភារៈជំនួស</strong></span></p></td></tr><tr><td><figure class=\"image image_resized\" style=\"width:79.09%;\"><img src=\"$url/storage/ckeditor-images/KywsOjLC_pngkey.com-red-solo-cup-png-1464623.png\"></figure><p style=\"text-align:center;\"><span><strong>កែវប្លាស្ទិក</strong></span></p></td><td><figure class=\"image image_resized\" style=\"width:63.35%;\"><img src=\"$url/storage/ckeditor-images/bYgxlhXA_Tour Stemless Champange.png\"></figure><p style=\"text-align:center;\"><span><strong>កែវថ្ម ឬពែង</strong></span></p></td></tr><tr><td><figure class=\"image image_resized\" style=\"width:65.96%;\"><img src=\"$url/storage/ckeditor-images/RC8ge7F7_32523_1000.png\"></figure><p style=\"text-align:center;\"><span><strong>កញ្ចប់ស្នោរ</strong></span></p></td><td><figure class=\"image image_resized\" style=\"width:30.88%;\"><img src=\"$url/storage/ckeditor-images/K7RDoM9V_Chan srak 2.png\"></figure><p style=\"text-align:center;\"><span><strong>ចានស្រាក់ / កញ្ចប់ក្រដាស / ស្លឹកចេក ស្លឹកឈូក</strong></span></p></td></tr><tr><td><figure class=\"image image_resized\" style=\"width:88.94%;\"><img src=\"$url/storage/ckeditor-images/YWOBSph1_Straws.H02.watermarked.2k.png\"></figure><p style=\"text-align:center;\"><span><strong>បំពង់បឺតប្លាស្ទិក</strong></span></p></td><td><figure class=\"image image_resized\" style=\"width:45.74%;\"><img src=\"$url/storage/ckeditor-images/4f5m9yFb_Fresh glass straw.png\"></figure><p style=\"text-align:center;\"><span><strong>បំពង់បឺត ដែលងាយរលាយបាន</strong></span></p></td></tr><tr><td><figure class=\"image image_resized\" style=\"width:66.69%;\"><img src=\"$url/storage/ckeditor-images/Hg9QYVdz_Plastic bag.png\"></figure><p style=\"text-align:center;\"><span><strong>ថង់ប្លាស្ទិក</strong></span></p></td><td><figure class=\"image image_resized\" style=\"width:80.13%;\"><img src=\"$url/storage/ckeditor-images/KNwBSIaM_recycle bags.png\"></figure><p style=\"text-align:center;\"><span><strong>ថង់ក្រណាត់ ឬក្រដាស</strong></span></p></td></tr><tr><td><figure class=\"image image_resized\" style=\"width:74.71%;\"><img src=\"$url/storage/ckeditor-images/232-2322857_see-the-waste-plastic-bottle.png\"></figure><p style=\"text-align:center;\"><span><strong>ដបទឹកសុទ្ធ</strong></span></p></td><td><figure class=\"image image_resized\" style=\"width:72.1%;\"><img src=\"$url/storage/ckeditor-images/metal bottles.png\"></figure><p style=\"text-align:center;\"><span><strong>ដបទឹកធ្វើពីលោហៈ</strong></span></p></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>",
                "sector_id": 1
